   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">H</seg>Appening vpon this Letter of M<seg rend="sup">r</seg>. CASAVBON <gap reason="foreign">
         <desc>〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉</desc>
      </gap>, (writ (as may appeare) vpon Ex<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>traordinary Occasion) together with some Funerall Lines, which (in regard of the Subiect) were a <hi>Piaculum</hi> to smother;<note n="*" place="margin">Quis Thrax defunctis, in Christo <gap reason="foreign">
            <desc>〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉</desc>
         </gap> neget?</note> I here offer them to thy courteous view. It is Piety (saith <hi>Naz.</hi>) to publish the deceaseds Vertues; yea, it is a meanes to increase grace in our owne selues. <hi>Vale; &amp; sanctas Vmbras, Ani<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>mam{que} planè diuinam, quâ par est Ʋeneratione, sequere.</hi>
   </p>
   <closer>
      <signed>I. M.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
